# Cloudflare Pages redirects. Copied verbatim into dist/ at build (public/ → site root).
#
# The root "/" must bounce to the default locale. Astro emits a dist/index.html
# meta-refresh page for this, but that flashes a blank "Redirecting…" page before
# it bounces. On Vercel, vercel.json's server-side 302 intercepts "/" first; this
# file is the Cloudflare equivalent. Cloudflare Pages follows _redirects rules
# before serving a static asset at the same path, so this wins over index.html.
/    /en/    302
# Short URL for the gallery → default-locale page (same no-flash reason as "/").
/hardware-gallery    /en/hardware-gallery/    302
